dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"印度政府再以國家安全為由，下令禁用43個中國應用程式，當中包括阿里巴巴旗下的支付寶和阿里速賣通(AliExpress)，以及香港公司Lalamove的印度業務。這是印度自6月與中國發生邊境衝突以來公布的第四批禁用中國應用程式(Apps)，令須下架的中國應用程式累積至267個。"},{"pid":"9f4f555dcb88235096ade6e64589cae7105d045e","tid":2302533,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"Give Chi na a taste of their own medicine<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570e8c5c58f19c008554fd04fc31fc674bad4bb5","tid":2302533,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5af2d141f1503a602c231da8d601b59c77592c9a","tid":2302533,"uid":61840,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"40461dfdac1b36406c03305c1b3cde8e96fb48ee","tid":2302533,"uid":8410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1fdd0a0c539009da1ba86dcdfebe56444b79e078","tid":2302533,"uid":11148,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xynC1OA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxynC1OA.jpg&h=5c0d489c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"諷刺地中國封的公司都係全球數一數二舔共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"其實係怕班支那仔<br />\n班支那仔乜事都講到去支那 郁下都話你辱華<br />\n而家d大公司就好似文明人比生番用錢操縱咁撚樣 好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋怕乜嘢小粉紅啫？啲小粉紅嘅嘴臉只會撻著囇全世界嘅網民一齊做奶茶聯盟去還拖姐嘛，根本唔會因為人多就要自我審查，佢哋凡事頼上支那咪佢做初一我哋做十五囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3d6a81750e02279cb5db69f62a90029d401ca8","tid":2302533,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=